Package: arco-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, arco-authors (= ${source:Version}), arco-devel (= ${source:Version}), arco-user (= ${source:Version})
Description: ARCO tools
 Metapackage for development and administrative tools for ARCO developers, and
 others.

Package: arco-authors
Replaces: arco-latex
Recommends: unoconv
Conflicts: arco-latex, arco-make
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, texlive-binaries, texlive-latex-extra,
 texlive-lang-spanish, texlive-latex-recommended, cm-super, inkscape, dblatex,
 rubber, netpbm, dia, aspell-en
Description: ARCO authors tools
 LaTeX and DocBook utilities and styles for ARCO authors.

Package: arco-pfc
Architecture: all
Depends:  ${misc:Depends}, arco-authors (= ${source:Version})
Description: LaTeX class and utilities for PFC typesetting.
 This package provides the arco-pfc LaTeX class created specifically to simplify
 PFC typesetting.

Package: arco-devel
Replaces: arco-make, arco-debian, arco-bashrc
